{"tid":1278011,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"我想寫隻game係關於模擬香港地產商的","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:41:56.000Z","uid":268272,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb83190049fa95486fa5d925a0d7ca3e070c9de","tid":1278011,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅小弟熱衷於模擬類遊戲<br />\n但眼見除咗Project Highrise以外<br />\n並沒有類似的遊戲<br />\n加上Project Highrise的遊戲方式<br />\n與歐美的發展模式相似<br />\n並不符合香港的發展模式<br />\n同時Project Highrise並沒有3D<br />\n並沒有足夠的幻想空間<br />\n<br />\n因此我希望能夠以香港的地產發展模式來製作一隻模擬類遊戲<br />\n能夠自行設計商場/私人住宅/寫字樓和相關的配套<br />\n如果有巴打有興趣參與創作嘅話<br />\n可以tg我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/jcleung215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjcleung215&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=5659f76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/jcleung215</a>"},{"pid":"aef3d37cd1b8e0a56b52c7d85f818dcd83dd2a69","tid":1278011,"uid":268272,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:39:57.000Z","msg":"軟件台開咗唔爭在開埋呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33ed696b460c26ccc3afdce53e9201472316e81","tid":1278011,"uid":12259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"遊戲有好多種既 紙牌遊戲係最易做的 你可以睇下鄭立介紹紙牌 今晚board野夜唔夜  有好多你諗到未諗都已經有 例如鐵路公司 表面上做交通 實質做政治任務 要買指定既火車頭"},{"pid":"1127669adebdcde54597a36f6bd0a0b5cdfac698","tid":1278011,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c33ed696b460c26ccc3afdce53e9201472316e81","tid":1278011,"uid":12259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"遊戲有好多種既 紙牌遊戲係最易做的 你可以睇下鄭立介紹紙牌 今晚board野夜唔夜  有好多你諗到未諗都已經有 例如鐵路公司 表面上做交通 實質做政治任務 要買指定既火車頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:45:59.000Z","msg":"師兄呢個提議幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係紙牌遊戲做唔到我嗰隻效果<img src